msgstr "Hwilas yn es ha trovya gorsavow radyo nowydh"

#: data/de.haeckerfelix.Shortwave.metainfo.xml.in.in:19
msgid ""
"Automatic recognition of tracks, with the possibility to save them "
"individually"
